{"kind":"overview","hierarchy":{"paths":[],"reference":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/tutorials\/table-of-contents-(discovery)"]}],"sections":[{"kind":"hero","title":"Swift Package Discovery Tutorial","backgroundImage":"ic_unified_ds.png","action":{"overridingTitle":"Get started","isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get started"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Discovering a new framework can be exciting and scary. Learn how you can embed and use OUDS Swift Package."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"With this tutorial you will learn fundamental concepts of Orange Unified Design System and discover the layers of this framework."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Theme, components, tokens… everything will be introduced!"}]}],"image":"ic_unified_ds.png"},{"content":[],"image":null,"kind":"volume","chapters":[{"name":"Import of the Swift Package and choose its librairies","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-1-package-and-librairies"],"image":"ic_unified_ds.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this chapter you will learn how to import the OUDS iOS Swift Package and which librairies it provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you should choose for your needs."}]}]},{"name":"Preparation of the theme","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme"],"image":"ic_theme_intro.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this chapter you will see how to instanciate a theme and inject it inside your app"}]}]},{"name":"